item.title: Not sure how I managed to catch my bus to DC this morning
item.description: I have no idea how I managed to get on my bus to DC this morning. My Citibike station I planned on, was full, then my phone is Unavailable until like 10:42 . Bus boards at 11:00am . Still got to find a citibike dock to park the bike, because the stolen citibike fee is $1,250. At 10:42 of course I open phone and have absolutely no cell service. The citibike station does not have a printed map on it.
